TomsSnippetizer
=========

This product is a single-file local replacement for code-screenshot tools.
It is conceptually inspired by carbon.now.sh by Dawn Labs, but contains
none of its source code; TomsSnippetizer is an independent reimplementation.

The implementation was developed with the assistance of Claude
(https://claude.ai/) by Anthropic.

The distributed file `tomssnippetizer_offline.html` includes the unmodified
source code of the third-party components listed below, each of which
remains under its original license. The complete, verbatim license texts
are reproduced in the LICENSE file that accompanies this distribution.


