--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Components NOT bundled but referenced for typography
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

TomsSnippetizer uses only operating-system-resident monospace fonts for code
display (Consolas, Menlo, SF Mono, DejaVu Sans Mono, Liberation Mono,
Lucida Console, Courier New, Monaco). No web fonts are loaded, embedded,
or otherwise included in the distribution.


